Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.20,0:02:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,通信卫星呢！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.89,0:03:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,受到了轨道上扬陆城的攻击
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.35,0:03:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,联合总部、支部的通信全部中断
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.38,0:03:10.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Alpha队长呼叫各机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.04,0:03:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,现在开始攻击！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.51,0:03:19.12,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:23.89,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行部队被全灭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.05,0:03:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,确认到了一架敌机
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.18,0:03:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Silver-22？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.38,0:03:30.30,Default,,0,0,0,,干扰吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.57,0:03:34.37,Default,,0,0,0,,先行的Silver小队好像已经和敌人接触了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.70,0:03:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,全机展开
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.93,0:03:37.12,Default,,0,0,0,,攻击一切敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.74,0:03:42.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是那家伙吗…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.58,0:03:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,队长！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.41,0:04:03.29,Default,,0,0,0,,愚蠢的原始人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.59,0:04:05.90,Default,,0,0,0,,跪在神的威光之下吧
